00:50:30.060 --> 00:50:32.029
(Likes, Junior Producer wins)

00:50:32.730 --> 00:50:34.965
(Votes, &lt;Alternate World&gt; 14,661
/ &lt;Maetdol Gala&gt; 15,187)

00:50:34.965 --> 00:50:37.535
(Votes, Junior Producer wins)

00:50:38.602 --> 00:50:41.305
(Truncated to two decimal places,
calculated as the sum of each weighted ratio)

00:50:43.240 --> 00:50:45.743
(Round 1, Producer Nah wins
by 0.42 percentage points)

00:50:45.743 --> 00:50:49.246
(Round 1 comes to an end)

00:50:50.781 --> 00:50:52.783
(July 10 (Fri), 6 PM)

00:50:53.384 --> 00:50:55.119
(Round 2)

00:50:56.253 --> 00:50:58.489
